Speaker A: Hello.
Speaker B: Hello.
Speaker A: Hi, I'm a speaker with Alistair.
Speaker B: Yes, this is Alistair.
Speaker A: Alistair, this is Rachna from Amber Student.
Speaker B: Pardon?
Speaker A: This is Rachna on behalf of University College London, powered by Amber Students. Yes, I received your inquiry that you were looking for accommodation.
Speaker B: Yes, I am looking for accommodation at the moment, yes.
Speaker A: Right. So I just wanted to help you regarding the same. I think you were looking for one of the two properties, I think London Nest, Lady Margaret and you were looking for Camden hall be present.
Speaker B: Yeah, I was looking at that before. Did I. Did I already book that by accident?
Speaker A: No, no, no, no, no. You haven't booked it, you were just looking at it and I think you just filled the basic details. So I just wanted to ask you, like, why are you still interested in the same property or you want to explore some more options which are available?
Speaker B: I was still just thinking about. I was just. I was just thinking about. About booking at London Nest, Margaret House or some other properties I was looking at. So.
Speaker A: So no, that. That's exactly my point. Like you're looking at certain options at the moment or you still want to like, explore or want me to share some options with you?
Speaker B: Oh, I want to explore my options for now and I can call you back if I end up looking at Lady Margaret House again.
Speaker A: Okay, perfect. I have dropped you WhatsApp. What we can do is when do you think we should connect back? Or what do you want me to share some options with you?
Speaker B: I don't. I don't need any options at the moment, thank you.
Speaker A: Okay, so when do you think we should connect back as a follow up? Just to know that, you know, if you need a help from mine at the moment.
Speaker B: I don't need help right now. If I'm 24 hours from now, I can. 24. I can, I can. I can call you back. 20. I can call you back 24 hours from now. Ish.
Speaker A: Okay, so I'll call you back in then. Let's connect in 24 hours.
Speaker B: Yeah. Unless. Unless I just. No longer. I'm looking at Lady Margaret as a house.
Speaker A: Do you want to lead with that by any chance? Or you just want to confirm me next 24 hours?
Speaker B: I'll just confirm you in the next 24 hours.
Speaker A: Perfect. Sounds good to me. I'll help you with that then.
Speaker B: Okay, bye.
Speaker A: Thank you.
